    <note type="biography">
        <p>German artist and photographer. Studied and worked in Hamburg; Dresden, 1843–8; Paris, 1850–3. Opened a photography studio in Hamburg in 1863 to supplement his income as a portrait artist. Returned to painting full-time in 1876.</p></note>
